For **Atelier Inkstar** customer-facing copy (website, listings, brand story), the founder's public name is **Vesper**.

Use `brand.founder.alias` from `@atelier-inkstar/config` — do not use Milo in public Atelier Inkstar text.

The user's personal name outside this brand context remains Milo.
